#~ msgid ""
#~ "If supported, this option allows you to hear audible clicks from your "
#~ "computer's speakers when you press the keys on your keyboard. In essence, "
#~ "this simulates the <quote>click</quote> of a mechanical type-writer. You "
#~ "can change the loudness of the key click feedback by dragging the slider "
#~ "button. Setting the volume to 0% by moving the slider to the left turns "
#~ "off the key click."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Jei palaikomas, šis funkcionalumas skleidžia garsą per jūsų garsiakalbius "
